{"tid":2149604,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解女仔幽默感唔及男仔？","createTime":"2020-08-10T13:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T13:04:39.000Z","uid":337157,"like":18,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"ecab554b1de0f2d7562b115436b0a1b1dda824eb","tid":2149604,"uid":337157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:14:31.000Z","msg":"發覺身邊啲囡囡幽默感硬係差啲咁<br />\n唔好話要佢地搞個gag 連get到個笑點都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女仔之間啲笑點多數要為內先會笑得出<span class=\"small\"><span class=\"navy\">(因為通常都係抽下水 mean下人咁)</span></span><br />\n唔同圈子跟本聽唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反男仔啲好笑位抽水之外仲會有啲gag夾集下咁<br />\n啲囡囡成日話要人有幽默感 但搞完個gag又冇人明算係咩意思喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講完要自己解釋埋點解好笑嗰下真係曬氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9bcdf2869f7a476db35bbf4b92633441c80378","tid":2149604,"uid":28068,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgix.bustle.com/inverse/f6/05/49/99/ed25/432d/a7ef/a86beb178596/sure-ejaculation-is-cool-but-what-about-ejaculation-that-includes-prostate-stimulation.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgix.bustle.com%2Finverse%2Ff6%2F05%2F49%2F99%2Fed25%2F432d%2Fa7ef%2Fa86beb178596%2Fsure-ejaculation-is-cool-but-what-about-ejaculation-that-includes-prostate-stimulation.gif&h=073219f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c83fae1426ac3ead38ba9d7fc84eb45a1881fdce","tid":2149604,"uid":342281,"like":57,"dislike":3,"score":54,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:21:14.000Z","msg":"你個問題好似係各自各講in-joke喎 唔關幽默感事<br />\nbtw 有啲男仔成日以為自己好幽默講埋啲on9嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830b4950428df96ca45461cb7d4db46bc98ce4d5","tid":2149604,"uid":271397,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:24:15.000Z","msg":"諗下點解靚仔多數都唔幽默就會明"},{"pid":"d05c4f16b3e3370ee9812